  <p> Search the L.M. Montgomery Research Centre, highlighting the University of Guelph's extensive collection of Montgomery memorabilia — including her private journals, scrapbooks, handiwork, photographs, and other records. For more information or more search options - <a href="http://images.ourontario.ca/uoguelph/search.asp">Visit our site</a>.</p>
   </fieldset>
</form>





Usage notes:   
1) the CSS and widget graphics are called from the VITAtoolkit server, where the Agency site originates.

2) the line above starting "form.minisearch-oo" needs to be on one line even though it may wrap in your display.

3) widget expects the site to provide an appropriate "branding" graphic  with the following specifications:
Search Widget Tile
• searchtile_286x73.jpg
• JPEG (.jpg)
• 286 pixels wide 73 pixels high
• optimized for web, so in the 12 – 20 KB file size range max.

Download the base wrapper for the branding slice here: 
<a href="http://www.ourontario.ca/portlets/_common/searchtile_286x73.psd">Get PSD template file</a>
